<main>
  <div class="container-fluid landing" id="who-am-i">
    <h1>Pedro Martin</h1>
    <h2>Web developer junior</h2>
    <p>London</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid landing" id="timer">
    <h1>I have been a coder</h1>
     <p id="timer-counter"> Since <%= Time.local(2015,07,17,16,00,00).ago_in_words %> </p>
  </div>
  
  <div id="lettuce" class="container-fluid landing">
    <h1>I am fresher than a lettuce</h1>
    <p><small>(I know, It was a really bad joke)</small></p>
    <p>But, I can do some things!</p>
    <p><strong>Check this out!</strong><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span><small>  (keep scrolling down)</small></p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid landing" id="code-test">
    <div class="row">
      <div  id="fizzbuzz" class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Give me a number and I will tell you if it is a Fizz or Buzz or neither</h2>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fizz_buzz" target="_blank" >What the heck is FizzBuzz?</a>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="text" id="FizzBuzz-number" class="form-control" placeholder="Your number" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="fizzButton">Go!</span>
        </div>
        <h2 id="fizzbuzz-result"></h2>
      </div>
      <div id="roman" class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Give me a number and I will convert to a Roman Numeral</h2>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roman_numerals" target="_blank" >What the heck is Roman Numeral?</a>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="text" id="roman-number" class="form-control" placeholder="Your number" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="romanButton">Go!</span>
        </div>
        <h2 id="roman-result"></h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid landing" id="projects">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h1><%= link_to('Projects', projects_path) %></h1>
        <div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="4"></li>
          </ol>

          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
              <img src="http://pataruco.s3.amazonaws.com/ga/glide/glide-screen.png" alt="Glide">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3>Glide</h3>
                <p> Realtime web application that allows you to experience different places (Google Maps API) through user generated experiences (Instagram API), made with Node.js and web sockets.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="http://pataruco.s3.amazonaws.com/ga/peace/peace-screen.png" alt="Peace">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3>The State of the world in peace</h3>
                <p>Atlas view app to raise awareness about the actual state of violence in the World using data from UN databases and D3.js library for visualisation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="http://pataruco.s3.amazonaws.com/ga/tic-tac-toe/tic-tac-toe-screen.png" alt="tic-tac-toe">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3>Back to school with tic-tac-toe</h3>
                <p>The classic tic tac toe code challenge made entirely with JavaScript and jQuery with primary school look</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="http://pataruco.s3.amazonaws.com/ga/villarock_app/villarock-screen.png" alt="villarock">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3>Villarock App</h3>
                <p>A weekly calendar for meals, listing recipes, ingredients and stock made with Rails, PostgreSQL, Rspec, Capybara</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="http://pataruco.s3.amazonaws.com/ga/Class_sounds/mario-screen.png" alt="Mario">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3>Mario bros sounds</h3>
                <p>Revisited Super Mario Bros sounds using SoundBoard JavaScript library</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Controls -->
          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>